he company operates through three segments electronic controls capacitors and battery chargers the electronic controls segment produces microprocessorbased control systems for zero emission and hybrid electric vehicles the electronic controls segment produces specialmetalized film capacitors for sale to electronic equipment manufacturers the capacitor segment produces specialmetalized film capacitors for sale to electronic equipment manufacturers the capacitor segment has a plant which is located at wales the battery chargers segment designs and manufactures battery chargers for electric vehicles the battery chargers segment has a plant which is located at italythe company designs manufactures and sells battery chargers for electric vehicles and power management and power source systems for industrial medical and telecom applications as well as electronic instrumentation for battery laboratories the companys customers are manufacturers of on and offroad vehicles including cars trucks buses motorcycles fork lift trucks aerial lifts mining vehicles airport tractors sweepers and other electrically powered vehicles it operates through its subsidiaries located in the united states england france south korea and japan joint venture located in china and through an international dealer network the company manufactures special metalized film capacitors that are used as components in the power electronics signaling and audio equipment marketsthe companys product categories include high voltage controllers which covers the voltage ranges from  volts v to over v direct current dc low voltage controllers which includes alternating current ac and dc motor controllers which are used in various traction and pump applications in some of the material handling vehicles as well as various onroad and offroad vehicles dcdc converters including a range of converters covering battery voltages from v to over v and output voltages from  to v battery chargers including a range of battery chargers and power management devices for both industrial onvehicle and automotive applications and the voltage ranges from  to v and power levels up to  kilowatts accessories which include a range of electronic gauges displays and other components and custom madethe companys products include gen hvlp and the high voltage low power hvlp ac motor controllers utilize its technology and work with permanent magnet and induction motors used in many bus and truck applications to deliver hybrid solutions by electrifying the auxiliary loads such as pumps air conditioning and fans the company offers ac controller products including gens gens gens and gens its other products include gen gen dc dragon millipak micropak powerpak gen hv dcdc dcdc w dcdc w ev fast charging stations multivoltage chargers high frequency switching high frequency igbthybrid intelligent battery module bcan smartview lcd display powergauge and pst power steering the company offers solutions to electric motorbikes pure electric vehicles hybrid performance cars zero emission performance cars integrated startergenerator isg bus and truck mild hybrid bus and trucks hybrid truck electrificationrefuse trucks and zero emissions heavy duty fork lift truckthe company competes with hitachi curtis instruments inc zapi spa sme srl bosch siemens continental and eaton corporation » full overview of sevph company address sevcon inc  northboro rdsouthborough   ma    p f  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation matthew boyle  paul farquhar  ryan morris  david steadman  glenn angiolillo  » more officers  directors sevcon inc news briefborgwarner enters agreement to acquire sevcon jul   briefsevcon and borgwarner provide update on merger agreement termination fee jul   briefsevcon signs definitive agreement to be acquired by borgwarner jul   briefsevcon buys remaining  pct interest in chinese joint venture jun   briefsevcon says has agreed to terminate its equity joint venture with fuhua glass jun  